# AODA accessibility

- Target WCAG 2.1 AA for popup, options, and injected bar/dialogs.
- Icon buttons need accessible names; pressed states use `aria-pressed` plus text, not color alone.
- Dialogs: `role="dialog"`, `aria-modal`, labelled title, Escape to close, initial focus.
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion`.
- Keep axe audits green (`npm run audit:a11y`).
